### Test Loan API Examples

### 1. Default 12-Month Loan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/emad_hamdy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalAmount": 12000.00,
  "customInstallments": null
}

### 2. Custom Installments - Sales Bonus Plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/emad_hamdy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalAmount": 15000.00,
  "customInstallments": [
    {
      "monthName": "Q1 2026 Bonus",
      "dueDate": "2026-04-15",
      "amount": 5000.00
    },
    {
      "monthName": "Q2 2026 Bonus", 
      "dueDate": "2026-07-15",
      "amount": 5000.00
    },
    {
      "monthName": "Q3 2026 Bonus",
      "dueDate": "2026-10-15", 
      "amount": 5000.00
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Custom Installments - Seasonal Plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/emad_hamdy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalAmount": 12000.00,
  "customInstallments": [
    {
      "monthName": "December 2025",
      "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
      "amount": 4000.00
    },
    {
      "monthName": "January 2026",
      "dueDate": "2026-01-31", 
      "amount": 2000.00
    },
    {
      "monthName": "February 2026",
      "dueDate": "2026-02-28",
      "amount": 2000.00
    },
    {
      "monthName": "March 2026",
      "dueDate": "2026-03-31",
      "amount": 4000.00
    }
  ]
}

### 4. Error Case - Amounts Don't Sum to Total
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/emad_hamdy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalAmount": 12000.00,
  "customInstallments": [
    {
      "monthName": "Test",
      "dueDate": "2026-12-31",
      "amount": 10000.00
    }
  ]
}
